org.ow2.proactive.scheduler.common

Interface ThirdPartyCredentials

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ISchedulerClient, Scheduler
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractSmartProxy, ClientBase, RestSmartProxyImpl, SchedulerClient, SchedulerNodeClient, SchedulerProxyUserInterface, SmartProxyImpl

    public interface ThirdPartyCredentials
    Third-party credentials are key-value pairs associated to a particular user and saved in the database. They can be used for instance to authenticate to third-party services in tasks.
